ygData.messageBody:
Hi Everyone,

I wanted to share with you a very nice EQ movie I found some
time ago online. I warn you though I found it to be very touching and
filled with emotion. It is a big flash movie and took me about an
hour to load on my 56k connection, but it is worth the wait, it is
truly unforgettable. When you first visit the link it will ask you to
download a japanese language pack, just click cancel to that, you can
view the movie perfectly fine without it. I hope you all enjoy it as
much as I did, please reply with your thoughts and feelings about the
movie after you watch it.

http://home.att.ne.jp/surf/mirage/memory_album.html
